This is a stable version of anyPaper.

anyPaper is a front-end for wallpapersetter, you can choose the screen size, background color, image position, wallpapersetter. Has 5 modes, fullscreen, normal, tiled, adjusted, sized.

Read NEWS to see whats new in this release.

For copyright information see COPYING

Compile and Install:

  $ ./configure
  $ make
  and then as root
  # make install

Configuration options:

  Use ./configure --help to see the full list of options

